feeling it all 💞

it’s been a month since I joined the @modern_nest // @marketbymodernnest team and I couldn’t be happier and more grateful for this opportunity. I feel so in my element surrounded by talented creatives that share my aesthetic appreciation, and it’s been so fun to learn a new industry while getting to put my skills towards a company I’ve followed along for years. I may have taken a step back from ‘influencer’ work, but I haven’t stopped creating, which has always been my love & passion. 🤍

Here are some photos from a shoot we did for Market by Modern Nest’s kids capsule Hatched Vol 2. If you love interior design,  beautiful homes, and a need for well-curated home goods make sure to follow @modern_nest @marketbymodernnest. I’ll be creating there!
